AIT - All Is Tag
================
:Author:    Nicolas Thouvenin
:Homepage:  http://ait.touv.fr[AIT home page]
:Email:     nthouvenin@gmail.com
:Key words: php, tags, store, search
:language:  php


Description 
-----------

AIT is PHP tag's engine. It provide a API, that can store in a database tags and items.
More information can be found at http://ait.touv.fr


License
-------

AIT is licensed under the LGPL version 2. For more information, see the attached COPYING file.


Downloading
------------

AIT is currently hosted at GitHub. It's source code can be found at
http://github.com/touv/ait. PEAR's package can be found at http://pear.pxxo.net/get/

You can also you the Pear's Installer :

......................................
$ pear channel-discover pear.pxxo.net
$ pear install pxxo/ait
......................................


